sentence: We will start by warming up!
We will rotate our head to warm up our neck.
Are you starting to feel warm now?
Let us do it a bit more advanced! Move your hand up. and bend to the side.
Let us do the same. but with the other hand!
Are you ready for the next one?
Thank you for today! I had so much fun! I hope all you cool people. want to work out. with me again!
